IN RE APPLICATION OF WILLIAM H. VON TISH. Submitted January term, 1925 Decided February 13, 1925.

Before Justices Tkknciiakd, Mixteen and Lloyd.

For the application, William E. Von Tisli (care Smith & Slingerland). Pee Cueiam.

Our examination of the annexed papers (correspondence with judges and letter of the clerk) satisfies us that the clerk is right in the ruling contained in his letter, and we decline to make any order.
